<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.5B.5BCharles_Mackay.7CMackay.2C_Charles.5D.5D1841"><a href="/wiki/Charles_Mackay" title="Charles Mackay">Mackay, Charles</a> (1841). <i><a href="/wiki/Extraordinary_Popular_Delusions_and_the_Madness_of_Crowds" title="Extraordinary Popular Delusions and the Madness of Crowds">Extraordinary Popular Delusions and the Madness of Crowds</a></i>. Wordsworth Editions. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1853263494" class="internal">ISBN 1-85326-349-4</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%5B%5BExtraordinary+Popular+Delusions+and+the+Madness+of+Crowds%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BCharles+Mackay%7CMackay%2C+Charles%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BCharles+Mackay%7CMackay%2C+Charles%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=1841&amp;rft.pub=Wordsworth+Editions&amp;rft.isbn=1-85326-349-4&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Crowd_psychology"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
