<ul>
<li><span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(English)</span> <i>Social influence and social change</i>, <a href="/wiki/Academic_Press" title="Academic Press">Academic Press</a>, 1976.</li>
